== Equipment Data Structure ==

Each equipment piece uses 8 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Equipment type (weapon/armor/etc)
|-
| $01 || 1 || Character equip flags (bitmask)
|-
| $02 || 1 || Primary stat (ATK for weapons, DEF for armor)
|-
| $03 || 1 || Secondary stat (EVA%, Magic DEF, etc)
|-
| $04-$05 || 2 || Price (buy price)
|-
| $06 || 1 || Element/status flags
|-
| $07 || 1 || Special properties
|}

