== Damage Formula ==

=== Physical Attack ===

<nowiki>
Damage = (ATK × 2) - (DEF × Modifier)
Critical = 2× Base Damage
Back Row = 50% Damage (except bows/whips)
</nowiki>

=== Elemental Modifiers ===

